OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry morning with
OL,6,Fbright and sunny spells. Remaining
OL,7,Fmostly dry through the afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome bright spells, but generally
OL,9,Fturning cloudier.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy this evening with
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain spreading northwards
OL,13,Fover mainly western parts. Overnight
OL,14,Fit will be cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain spreading to all parts.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,18,Foutbreaks of rain. Becoming drier with
OL,19,Fbright spells for a time in the
OL,20,Fafternoon, best of these in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
